professional degree list.
HJR40 INTRODUCED
29 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, That copies of this
30 resolution be transmitted to the U.S. Secretary of
31 Education, the Alabama Congressional Delegation, and
32 relevant federal and congressional committees.
